ZH: 大约十年前，这座小镇上发生了一场可怕的火灾。
EN: About ten years ago, a terrible fire broke out in this small town.

ZH: 昨天在公园里发生了一起严重的车祸。
EN: A serious car accident happened in the park yesterday.

ZH: 他们之间发生了一场严重的争吵。
EN: A serious argument occurred between them.

ZH: 这个城市最近频繁发生恐怖袭击。
EN: The city has recently been plagued by frequent terrorist attacks.

ZH: 请告诉我发生了什么事情。
EN: Please tell me what happened.

ZH: 我们不知道下一次会发生什么。
EN: We don't know what will happen next.

ZH: 她说发生一场车祸并不是很严重。
EN: She said that the car accident wasn't very serious.

ZH: 每天都有许多事情在这个城市发生。
EN: Many things happen in this city every day.

ZH: 发生变化的时候，我们需要适应。
EN: We need to adapt when changes happen.

ZH: 请告诉我你认为发生了什么事情。
EN: Please tell me what you think happened.

ZH: 发生在我身边的一切让我感到困惑。
EN: Everything happening around me makes me confused.

ZH: 那天他突然发生了变化，变得更加成熟。
EN: He suddenly changed that day, becoming more mature.

ZH: 我们需要探究事故发生的原因。
EN: We need to explore the reasons behind the accident.

ZH: 这个社区最近发生了很多抢劫案。
EN: There have been many robberies in this community recently.

ZH: 我没有料到这样的事情会发生在我身上。
EN: I never expected something like this to happen to me.

ZH: 当你不在身边时，一切都可能发生。
EN: Anything can happen when you're not around.

ZH: 他经常讲述那天在他家附近发生的事情。
EN: He often talks about what happened near his house that day.

ZH: 这是一个不断发生变化的世界。
EN: This is a world that is constantly changing.

ZH: 请告诉我发生了什么使你这么生气。
EN: Please tell me what happened to make you so angry.

ZH: 他们不想让事故发生在任何人身上。
EN: They do not want the accident to happen to anyone.
